{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/chronic-aortic-dissection-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/chronic-aortic-dissection-and-driving","title":"Chronic aortic dissection and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T12:53:57+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2255","business_proposition":false,"description":"You may need to tell DVLA if you have chronic aortic dissection - if you do, download the correct form to let them know","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You may need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have chronic aortic dissection.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>You don&rsquo;t need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. However, you should only start driving again after you have received satisfactory treatment. If you&rsquo;re unsure, check with your doctor.</p>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form VOCH1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065302.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘VOCH1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 394KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:10:22+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:13:59+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Surrendering your driving licence","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:09:58+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:11:37+00:00"}]}